The paper discusses query optimization in databases with inconsistencies or uncertainties, which is a common issue in database management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases). The paper also mentions the use of data mining techniques, which suggests a connection to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The evaluation of the impact of using invalid semantic knowledge suggests a connection to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of Belief Logic Programming suggests a connection to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
